{"id":147821,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：南宁一农药厂爆炸引发大火/","date":"2011-04-26T07:00:25Z","modified":"2011-04-26T07:00:25Z","title":"简讯：南宁一农药厂爆炸引发大火","content":"<div>\n<p>中国广西南宁市邕宾路6号的金穗农药厂仓库周一（25日）下午发生爆炸引起大火，现已扑灭，事故造成3人受伤。</p>\n<p>据官方新华社报道，这次大火的过火面积近3000平方米，两间仓库因火倒塌。</p>\n<p>报道引述专家说，现场的空气中监测到了甲醛和磷化氢，但含量对公众健康安全未造成威胁。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/52PMxvEQl5MJdHvx90qSal2JjLE/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/52PMxvEQl5MJdHvx90qSal2JjLE/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/52PMxvEQl5MJdHvx90qSal2JjLE/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/52PMxvEQl5MJdHvx90qSal2JjLE/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/pm2XqktbcaQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}